# Adding Machine Learning Capabilities
To add machine learning capabilities to your chatbot, you can use Google's AI Platform. 
This will allow you to train your chatbot to better understand user input and provide more accurate responses.

# Enhancing User Experience
You can enhance the user experience of your chatbot by adding rich media, such as images or videos, to your responses. 
You can also use Google Cloud's Translation API to translate responses into different languages based on the user's preference.

# Continue Monitoring and Analyzing
Monitoring and analyzing the performance of your chatbot using Stackdriver and Google Analytics. 
This will allow you to identify issues and improve the user experience.
